b_paragraph\"><strong>Dr. Unit's Private Gallery:</strong> A gallery showcasing how each giantess was captured!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">By reaching 100% progress in each stage, a special animation will be unlocked. Progress is based on the amount of money raised, which is cumulative, so with skill, you can unlock new content in just a few tries - or even on your first!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Streaming-friendly censored mode</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>15 Cards and 32 achievements</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054690/extras/005.png?t=1736627857\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Featuring visual novel story segments with animated character sprites, seamlessly blends story and gameplay to deliver the ultimate analog arcade experience for the modern era!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054690/extras/firehawk-characters.png?t=1736627857\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054690/extras/001.gif?t=1736627857\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Easy Rider","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2054690/e5f267e229c751c2c5e31f0c9295a17312ed8042.jpg"},{"name":"Bounty Hunter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2054690/5d6dc4074fc16f85c0679d28ca17b4897391e1c5.jpg"},{"name":"Shameless Fighter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2054690/59fae218ec628f4958a65d6dac98878bd6536c0f.jpg"},{"name":"Giantess Pleaser","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2054690/25cc817158b5a4bca3628e1f029c014acc752add.jpg"